06:43.020 --> 06:44.100
[Apakah dia sudah tahu]

06:44.100 --> 06:45.539
[kalau aku menulis tentang dirinya di novel?]

06:48.020 --> 06:48.660
[Aku...]

06:51.179 --> 06:52.539
[Aku sudah ketahuan.]

07:05.419 --> 07:06.140
Terima kasih.

07:06.939 --> 07:07.460
Silakan.

07:08.820 --> 07:09.499
Guru Qu.

07:10.179 --> 07:11.580
Jika dia tiba-tiba muncul,

07:11.900 --> 07:12.780
